    <li>Calm[T] - calm the target, making them like the caster. (Caelum Mandatum Mens Beatitas)</li>
    <li>Walk - walk for PSID10 minutes through the Aether. You can still peer into the material world by looking at what those whos bodies are still in the physical world's souls see. [Look through their bodies eyes through their soul] (Caelum Mutare Vis Deorum Sanguinem Alacer </li>
    <li>Truth? - Determine if the target is telling the truth. (Caelum Disco Mens Auctoritas)</li>
    <li>Convince - Convince the target of what the caster is saying. (Caelum Mutare Mens Pertinax)</li>
    <li>Track - Track a target for (2 * (1 d * (10/per PSI point)) * (1D20 * 100) * 2) Meters and is persistant, requiring the target to pass 2 DC 8 + Effect Psi checks to avoid being tracked. (Caelum Disco [Creaturae | Hominum] Dilata Immensa Dilatanda Pertinax)</li>
