<h3>Material Ring</h3>
<p></p>
<ul>
    <li>Mold Earth - Mold 1 + Psi point D meters of Earth. (Verus Mutare Terra)</li>
    <li>Create Food - Create enough food for 1+PSi Point D meals. (Verus Aedificate Planta)</li>
    <li>Create Water - Create 1+PSi Point D Liters of water. (Verus Aedificate Liquidum)</li>
    <li>Create Weapon - Create a weapon of 1D + Effect + Psi Point Tech Level . (Verus Aedificate Molior)</li>
    <li>Super Speed - Multiply your movement by the number of psi points used (Verus Mutare Hominum)</li>
    <li>Change Surface[T] - Heat or Free Freeze a surface by 1D * (-)100 degrees Celsius (Verus Putridus Terra mutare Damno Elementum)</li>
</ul>

<h3>Nether Ring</h3>
<p></p>
<ul>
    <li>Speak with Corpse[T] - Speak with the brain within a corpse. (Exanimum Disco Mens Mortuis)</li>
    <li>Raise Corpse[T] - Bring a corpse under your command. (Exanimum Mandatum Hominum Mortuis)</li>
    <li>Ward from Dead - Protect an area from the dead being able to enter. (Exanimum Aedificate Vis Mortuis)</li>
    <li>Rest Spirit - Banish a spirit to the Nether. (Exanimum Putridus Mens Mortuis)</li>
    <li>Unbind[T] - Remove a ward or curse from an object. (Exanimum Putridus Vis)</li>
    <li>Curse[T] - Apply a <a href="/Rules/Magic/Curses">Curse</a> to an object. (Exanimum Aedificate Vis Maledictum)</li>
</ul>

<h3>Abyss Ring</h3>
<p></p>
<ul>
    <li>Destroy Physical[T] - Destroy something in the material Plane, the target can resist on an Endurance 10+ check. (Exitium Putridus [Creaturae, Liquidum, Aura, Planta, Terra, Molior])</li>
    <li>Destroy Spiritual - Destroy something in the spiritual Plane, the target can resist on an Psi 10+ check.  (Exitium Putridus [Vis, Mens])</li>
    <li>Fast Forward[T] - Accelerate something into a further state of entropy. (Exitium Mutare [Creaturae, Hominum, Planta,  Mens, Molior, Terra])</li>
    <li>Empty Soul - Empty the soul of something in the material plane. Target can resist with a Psi 10+ check. (Exitium Mandatum Vis)</li>
    <li>Extinguish[T] - Extinguish a flame. (Exitium Putridus Ignis)</li>
    <li>Remove from reality[T] - Remove something from ever having existed in this timeline, is cast with a DC of 12+, and can be resisted with a PSI 6+ Effect (Exitium Putridus [creaturae, hominum])</li>
</ul>

